<td tEditID="c1r1" style=" background-color:#FFFFFF; bEditID:r3st1; color:#000000; bLabel:main; font-size:12pt; font-family:arial;" aEditID="c1r1" locked="1" >
<![CDATA[<p class="MsoNormal"><span style="font-size: 12pt; line-height: 17.12px; background: white;">Hi {!Lead.FirstName},<br></span><br><font face="arial">I’ve not been able to reach you to provide you with a quote for your business insurance.</font><br><br><font face="arial" style="font-size: 12pt;">It would be useful to know more about your business, so I can understand what cover you might require.<br></font><span style="font-size: 12pt;"><font face="arial"><br></font><font face="Arial, sans-serif">Some key benefits of buying from Kingsbridge are:</font></span></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="font-size: 12pt;"></p><ul style="font-size: 12pt;"><li><font face="Arial, sans-serif"><b>Packaged products from industry-leading A-rated insurers –&nbsp;</b>We offer a range of products that are tailored to specific sectors and job roles.</font></li><li><font face="Arial, sans-serif"><b>Flexible payment options –&nbsp;</b>We offer multiple ways to pay for your policy, including monthly payment options.&nbsp;</font></li><li><font face="Arial, sans-serif"><b>Competitively priced cover -&nbsp;</b>We make sure our prices remain competitive for all our customers, whether they’re new to us or not.</font></li><li><font face="Arial, sans-serif"><b>Outstanding customer service -&nbsp;</b>Our experienced customer service team are here to help you with cover that suits your needs. But don’t just take it from us, why not take a look at our 10,000+&nbsp;<a href="https://www.feefo.com/en-GB/reviews/kingsbridge-contractor-insurance?displayFeedbackType=SERVICE&amp;timeFrame=YEAR">Feefo reviews</a>, with an average customer satisfaction score of 4.8/5.</font></li></ul><div style="font-size: 12pt;"><font face="Arial, sans-serif">However, it would be good to discuss your requirements to make sure this is the best policy for you.</font><b style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif;">&nbsp;Is there a good time for me to give you a call?<br></b><font style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif;"><br>Alternatively, you can contact me on&nbsp;</font><b style="font-size: 12pt;">01242 808 740</b><font style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif;">. Our office is open between the hours of 8:00am-5:30pm, Monday-Friday.&nbsp;<br></font><font style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif;"><br>You can also get a quote online via our website&nbsp;</font><span style="font-size: 12pt;"><a href="http://www.kingsbridge.co.uk/">www.kingsbridge.co.uk</a></span><font style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif;">.<br></font><font face="arial"><br>I look forward to hearing from you soon.&nbsp;<br></font><span style="font-size: 12pt; background-color: white;"><br>Kind regards,<br></span><font style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif;"><br>{!User.FirstName}<br></font><font style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif;">Sales Team<br></font><font style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif;"><br>E: salesteam@kingsbridge.co.uk<br></font><font style="font-size: 12pt;">T:&nbsp;</font><font style="font-size: 12pt;">01242 808740</font></div>]]></td>
</tr>
</table>